This is a test project based on requirements provided at http://shoestore-manheim.rhcloud.com/

Automation tests are written in Selenium using Java along with testNG framework. Project build is done using Maven and test execution covered by Maven surefire plugin.

Default build and test execution command: mvn clean test

Default browser used for all tests is Firefox. To run tests in Chrome browser, specify the browser name in shoestoreconfig.properties file and execute

Test execution using surefire plugin by default is sequential. Enabled parallel execution, so currently tests run classes in parallel

Minimum requirements:

Maven 3.0.5
JRE 1.7
Selenium 2.53
